<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>What?  Clerics can enchant jewelry too?</font></td></tr></table>
<BR>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Velisaris</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-10-30 17:14:48</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>No, clerics do not "enchant" gems..they "imbue" them. Imbued gems are used to make racial armor.</font></td></tr></table>
